SNO+ Dispatcher
===============

Installation
------------

To install the dispatcher library::

    $ git clone git@github.com:snoplus/disp.git
    $ cd disp/src
    $ make

If you want to build RAT with dispatch support, you should add the following
line to your ~/.bashrc file::

    export DISPROOT=[path/to/disp]

where `[path/to/disp]` is the path to the root directory of the disp package.

Running the Dispatcher
----------------------

To run the dispatcher, simply run::

    $DISPROOT/bin/dispatch

To run the dispatcher as a daemon::

    nohup $DISPROOT/bin/dispatch &>[path/to/logfile] &
